# Email Template Design

## Overview

This project was created as part of the CodSoft UI/UX Internship Program. The objective was to design a professional onboarding email template for CareerSphere, a career development platform that helps students and professionals connect, learn, and grow. The design focuses on user engagement, visual hierarchy, and clear call-to-action elements.

## Features

* Modern and professional email layout
* Personalized welcome message
* Strong call-to-action buttons
* Clear content hierarchy
* Career-focused information sections
* User testimonial section for credibility
* Social media integration
* Responsive and user-friendly design

